title: Oberweimar station
text: Oberweimar station is a <a href="railway%20station">railway station</a> in the <a href="Oberweimar">Oberweimar</a> district in the <a href="List%20of%20cities%20and%20towns%20in%20Germany">city</a> of <a href="Weimar">Weimar</a>, located in <a href="Thuringia">Thuringia</a>, <a href="Germany">Germany</a>.
